---
/* Astro Component Script */
---
<section class="about py-16 px-6 bg-white text-black">
    <!-- Title and Introduction -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Bethelor.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium">
            Home Remodeling with Integrity, Craftsmanship, and Vision.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <!-- Left Column: Text -->
        <div>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                At Bethelor, we specialize in home remodeling and improvement services across Maryland. From kitchens and bathrooms to complete home renovations, we bring precision, passion, and personalized attention to every project—big or small.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6">
                Founded by skilled professionals with years of hands-on experience, Bethelor is built on trust, hard work, and a clear commitment to quality. We work closely with homeowners to transform their spaces with smart design, durable materials, and reliable results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
                Our team takes pride not only in what we build—but in how we make our clients feel throughout the process.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column: Statistics -->
        <div class="flex space-x-6 justify-center">
            <!-- Completed Projects -->
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
                    +12
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium">Done Projects</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Years of Experience -->
            <div class="text-center">
                <div class="bg-black text-white rounded-full w-24 h-24 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold">
                    +23
                </div>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium">Years of Experience</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image Gallery -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Image 1 -->
        <img
                src="/images/cabinetry.jpg"
                alt="Professional installing cabinetry"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md"
        />
        <!-- Image 2 -->
        <img
                src="/images/planning.jpg"
                alt="Team member working on a project"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md"
        />
        <!-- Image 3 -->
        <img
                src="/images/construction.jpg"
                alt="Worker during construction"
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md"
        />
    </div>
</section>